name: Bape x Pokemon x A Tiny City. Print 1. Ltd ed, 100.
description: A Tiny City Printing Press is excited to fan the flames surrounding our designs for the Bape x Pokemon collaboration. We've been allowed to produce one of the designs that has already been shown on several publications on the internet as a limited edition screen-print poster. This print is the first in hopefully a large series of prints surrounding the Bape x Pokemon collaboration. This print is limited to 100, numbered and stamped. Accept no imitations! 18" x 24" 3 color print on French Paper Glo-tone Yellow 65 lb. This is the US edition, so there's USA shipping only - Japan Edition soon!
